{"tid":818519,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"救災太慢挨轟 台灣駐大阪辦事處長蘇啓誠自殺身亡","createTime":"2018-09-14T07:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T15:59:43.000Z","uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1be4b30f025441b9c6bec194403570f701989bd8","tid":818519,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T07:19:18.000Z","msg":"颱風、強震上周連續重創日本，上千台灣旅客受困日本，有網友爆料求助於大阪辦事處要求代訂旅館卻遭冷語相待，讓駐日代表處被罵慘，結果約一周後，駐大阪辦事處處長蘇啓誠今天竟意外身亡。據傳蘇啟誠是因壓力過大輕生，外交部對此一不幸事件表達最深切的悲痛及惋惜。<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/politics/realtime/20180914/1429786\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2Frealtime%2F20180914%2F1429786&d=dIfxOrxKFTLYvKLYCu4EvVzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=988b37de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2Frealtime%2F20180914%2F1429786&h=7a5aa577\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/politics/realtime/20180914/1429786</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180914/640_8f6d0f44c19043b1177fe8fc09776089.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180914%2F640_8f6d0f44c19043b1177fe8fc09776089.jpg&h=6db680e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個台灣都屌大陸人有車係關西機場載人走而台灣冇安排，根本是假新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71044f7ed9af4a8bdb8501b3793bf7388a37569d","tid":818519,"uid":155818,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T07:20:14.000Z","msg":"台狗害死人<br />\n無辦法<br />\n民智未開"},{"pid":"5e02fc106f580cec1cfe7dd9fe8a4dc2665f1bee","tid":818519,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T07:35:00.000Z","msg":"咁易睇唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ad3a2da507c140073db0da4ccf4408ee9b9ee0","tid":818519,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T07:36:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>綠營人士強調，大家都在罵謝長廷，但此次問題最大的還是在大阪辦事處長身上，卻沒人知道處長是誰</strong></span>，況且謝身為駐日代表根本管不到這麼細，也管不到大阪轄區，除非辦事處長改成政務任用，駐外代表有全權考核辦事處人員權力，才能權責相符，否則不管由誰來做都是背黑鍋。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民進黨立委蔡適應則認為</span></strong>，台灣長期來台日關係是長期重要一環，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">這次淹水地區是大阪辦事處轄區，如同謝說，大阪末梢神經慢半拍，讓民眾詬病</span></strong>，相較之下札幌辦事處人員就較為認真，不過民眾不滿情緒也是鞭策政府原動力，相關單位需要檢討改進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6656/3357302\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6656%2F3357302&d=dIfxOrxKFTLYvKLYCu4EvVzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=01c400a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6656/3357302</a><br />\n<br />\n「下屬的功績是上司的功勞，上司的過錯是下屬的責任」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"175af4aa88e48a2380b26611d854e918b18ab07d","tid":818519,"uid":96453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T15:59:43.000Z","msg":"台狗腦殘 支那派車接人d假新聞都信。。"}]}